{"tid":82562,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"性價比係唔係蝗語?","createTime":"2017-01-16T05:04:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-16T08:48:59.000Z","uid":60074,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6df779af491fe2326ee3f5f1dd43bd6d35507571","tid":82562,"uid":60074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T05:04:25.000Z","msg":"前派嗌緊咩咩字詞係咪蝗語個期見到有人話性價比係咪蝗語<br />\n個詞語以前未見過，但第一次睇就即刻明(性能同價錢既比例)<br />\n以前啲人又點講啲數碼產品值唔值<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535120720eaf08c18102e78e18456c27bf87038a","tid":82562,"uid":3852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T05:08:43.000Z","msg":"有大陸人濫用=蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c305bb373381701c1f314eec2bc62503302d7d2c","tid":82562,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T05:10:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有大陸人<del>濫</del>用=蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"6443367afcb6c71e5b1a3a523e85523221e077f3","tid":82562,"uid":20625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T05:17:14.000Z","msg":"英文好似係price-performance ratio<br />\n如果你接字直譯，應該唔係"},{"pid":"dd36c86e0195864f5acf89b678c67c6a1b7086eb","tid":82562,"uid":60074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T05:19:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有大陸人濫用=蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實個人覺得好反智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時日變遷，語文都要進步會有新既字詞去形容新事物，例如以前冇偽毒，偽文青咁既詞語。<br />\n眼見好多巴打見個字詞係大陸落黎既就屌左先<br />\n我睇法係如果一個字詞本身粵語係冇既，就算有個新字詞係比大陸用左先，只要個字詞意思係通順都可以用<br />\n但係有薯仔唔用用土豆有多士唔用用吐司個啲就仆街死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acc60e769c4c0b689a39353b25130e3f4496f29f","tid":82562,"uid":29297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T05:20:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有大陸人濫用=蝗語